702153f-b.title: Bronx: White Plains Road - 216th Street (East)
702153f-b.text:
(1)
White Plains Road, adjoining the N.W. corner of East 216th Street,
showing the Emanuel Baptist Church.
November 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, as viewed northward from the corner.
November 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

700330f-a.title: Bronx: 216th Street (East) - White Plains Road
700330f-a.text:
(1)
715 to 727 East 216th Street, north side, between White Plain
Road and Barnes Ave., showing, at Nos. 717-719 (building with columns),
Hebron Lodge No. 813, F. \& A. M. The view is in an easterly direction.
November 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
An eadlusive view of the Bebron Lodge No. 813, F. \& A.W.
May 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

702154f-a.text:
3667 White Plains Road, south of the S.W. corner of East 216th
Street. On the right apnears the rear of Public School No. 13,
